{"tid":1850801,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家底子裡都係支那人 應該人道毀滅","createTime":"2020-01-29T17:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T17:21:51.000Z","uid":140848,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"99bdd180ea8fd713077d7427fc3510eac87e2d6c","tid":1850801,"uid":140848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:10:44.000Z","msg":"越南停發中國公民旅遊簽證 包括港澳<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850169\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850169</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇完呢個post既comment 發覺好多連登仔都係支那人<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">越南好明顯唔想你地黎傳染肺炎</span></span></strong> 你班連登仔問長問短 又話book左點算 又話自己有bno係英國人 試圖走漏洞 <br />\n<br />\n咁同d湖北人千方百計想入香港一樣 咁係咪佢地話book哂機票酒店就可以求香港俾佢地入？又同d支那雙非買外國護照黎香港生仔一樣 總之就走漏洞 以為自己好撚醒！<br />\n<br />\n一句講哂 大家都係支那人屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbb2684bd6ad71a6074dea483f3dd8f2e47d5ce","tid":1850801,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:11:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/308/5d9705d903228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F308%2F5d9705d903228.jpg&h=786cb045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">種族清洗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過邊境不設防<br />\n高調宣揚非本地人士免費優先治療武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓄意引導大量染病支那人來港<br />\n摧毀香港已經長期超負荷的醫療系統，令香港人大規模感染<br />\n而無法隔離或治理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n中共打算將香港將變成武漢，市民無法睇醫生，橫屍街頭<br />\n意圖對香港人進行大屠殺</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n香港人，仲唔反佢老母？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0739ca97a2f77da975cf800abe4394f788602923","tid":1850801,"uid":140848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:12:17.000Z","msg":"順便一提 越南見你bno簽發地係hk或者見你咁既柒樣由hk飛黎 一樣可以原機送你返黎啦柒頭港豬"},{"pid":"9adddb37afba3e78e92b244111b26ebef9e3a324","tid":1850801,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:12:19.000Z","msg":"醫護手足 點可以因為一場本可以封關避免嘅病毒而賭上生命<br />\n我地仲未光復到香港啊..<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥  借刀殺人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850782</a>"},{"pid":"720827d79e9c2a75787b7a98d37b28f03e6d18d3","tid":1850801,"uid":140848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T17:15:07.000Z","msg":"港豬已偷偷留下負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ea80aa6fa